result.title: 1984 - 1984 Centre for Environment, Fisheries & Aquaculture Science (Cefas) Southern North Sea and English Channel Plankton Survey - RV Cirolana 01/84
result.name: 1984-1984-centre-for-environment-fisheries-aquaculture-science-cefas-southern-north-sea-a-01-84
result.notes:
Analysis results from a survey carried out in January 1984 in the Southern 
Bight area of the North Sea and in the eastern English Channel. Species 
targetted were herring larvae and plaice eggs. Plankton samples were collected 
at planned sites. This data consists of the numbers of plaice eggs, along with 
associated positional data and volumes filtered.
